It is designed with tightly-binned surface-mount LEDs paired with fine-tuned, custom-designed TIR optics. This results in improved color reproduction and increased brightness that provides a longer throw. The Brick delivers a 100W tungsten equivalent output at a 36 beam angle and is flicker-free at any frame rate or shutter angle.   The Brick LED Light features an ultra-smooth 100 to 0% brightness dimmer. It also has a dedicated power button, allowing you to maintain your settings when you turn the light off.
